{
  "stem": "11998.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or I would go and attach myself to a lady and pretend that I was with her.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So as to-- so you learn a mechanism in order to survive, in a hostile environment.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, many times.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Punched, and beaten, and-- you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that was the reality of the situation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we would-- well, if we were together, we would fight them back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Either with stone, or with sticks, or with our pencil holders, which was our defense mechanism.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we did not take it quietly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that usually ended up that it escalated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, if they found you, they said, oh, he's the guy that we fought yesterday, so let's beat him up.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so that's how  it went.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, this happened mainly in like-- it happened in 1930-- the ones I remember-- it's already 1938, the beginning of '39 when there was an awful lot of Nazi propaganda coming through into Poland and against Jews.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were already signs on the-- on the stores.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father was beaten up on the street because he was a Jew.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was-- windows were broken in the stores, and there was already [NON-ENGLISH], you know, described on the--",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Down with the Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was a lot of graffiti on the storefronts.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And people were-- generally, Jews were harassed by the--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--By the people who lived in our town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the town that we lived in, as I indicated, there was-- before 1918, it was part of Germany.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then [NON-ENGLISH] of 1920, it became Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So there was a lot of German nationals there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when the war was about to break out, they came out like-- they came out like flies to the light.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
